PEPE WICK

Pepe Frog has many enemies because he is popular. Blasphemed, threatened with Knife, sent a Bazooka, threatened with Kris (Indonesian cultural weapon), exposed to Covid-19 and affected by supernatural disorders (Santet, magical rituals in Indonesian). He is fully supported in the Ethereum Blockchain network so he continues to survive.
